starvationevasion.client.GUIOrig.Graphs

Class GraphManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • starvationevasion.client.GUIOrig.Graphs.GraphManager

  • public class GraphManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Graph Manager which handles all of the graphs attached to the GUIOrig Has functions which allows the client to add data to a graph or methods for the graph node in the GUIOrig to get the linechart which needs to be displayed
